{"Sid":0,"Did":118265,"Id":"282784","Title":"石牌金面大觀","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-23/d5762221-76ee-4739-b042-ac0232cc08bc/collection/0a03e0e4-9e00-402b-a7de-905c9eb0204b/108-sea-pa-178-201909171433515d806a6446daa0.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n1898年北宜公路動工，徵用歸順土匪與役；1899年五月開通，於湖底嶺之路頂上設有一小型公園，可遠眺攬勝。1900年完工時，宜蘭廳長西鄉菊次郎在公園內立石，刻有「湖底嶺開路碑」，而由台灣總督兒玉源太郎篆額『平塹雲開』，記載當時開路的艱辛過程，後人便稱立碑處為「石牌」。1962年9月林才添縣長在石背銘以「金面大觀」；1965年7月陳進東縣長將西鄉碑文磨掉，改刻「亢懷今古」四字，原先的碑文已蕩然無存。石牌因位於北宜公路的最高點，景觀氣勢萬千，於1954年被選定為新蘭陽八景之一。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.7930247","Keyword_Latitude":"24.8507676","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/A2C79436-0F02-49A5-8390-1154D3C239DD","Original_Identifier":"282784","Keyword_Subject_1":"空間、地域與遷徙","alias":"","Keywords":"亢懷今古 / 北宜公路 / 石牌 / 金面大觀 / 湖底嶺開路碑","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2020/02/23 23:53:41","timelines":"","place":"","address":"宜蘭縣頭城鎮北宜公路","longitude":"121.7930247","latitude":"24.8507676","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"","writer":"莊文生;鐘碧娟;謝淑娟","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-02-23/d5762221-76ee-4739-b042-ac0232cc08bc/collectionOpen/34061871-4d0e-4d7f-9ebe-9ae06fea4312/108-sea-pa-178-re-201909200929095d841c7403d2f0.jpg"}}